{
  "title": "Fried Greek Fish Stir-Fry",
  "description": "A fresh and silky date-night dish featuring a deliciously crisp fried fish base with the addition of dijon mustard for a unique twist in a pescatarian-friendly recipe.",
  "cuisine": "greek",
